Our Milestones

Phase 2

Product Expansion and Market Positioning

  • Enhancing Marketing Efforts
  • Establishing Strategic Partnerships
  • Publishing Security Reports Based on User Scans
  • Beta Release of Wallet Analyzer on Website
  • Development of Cross-Chain Bridging
Phase 3

Ecosystem Growth & Token Utility

  • Launch Pro Features including wallet monitoring, real-time risk alerts, and downloadable security reports
  • Integrate the $SAFEHEX token to unlock premium scans, report access, and scan credit tiers
  • Launch an advanced wallet analyzer with built-in PnL tracking and trade history insights
  • Introduce a community referral and rewards program to drive user growth and incentivize ecosystem participation
Phase 4

Scaling, AI Evolution & Institutional Adoption

  • Expand SafeHex AI to support multi-chain scanning (Solana, Base, Arbitrum, Avalanche, etc.)
  • Continuously train and improve the AI threat engine using real-world scan data
  • Launch a mobile-optimized SafeHex AI dashboard for on-the-go wallet safety
  • Develop a Security Partner Network (wallets, dApps, launchpads, infra tools) for embedded integrations
  • Begin compliance and institutional onboarding offering enterprise-grade wallet security and risk reports for funds, projects, and exchanges
